title: The Rock is in Fortnite? - Kinda Funny Games Daily 03.19.21
description:
Greg and Bless talk about the rumor that the Rock is in Fortnite, PlayStation buying EVO, and more!

00:00:00 - Start
00:03:00 - Housekeeping
The Kinda Funny Wild Aces are in the FCF Championship. Come call the plays as we take on the Glacier boys this Saturday on twitch.tv/kindafunnygames at 6:30 p.m. PT!
If the MCU and DCEU are more your things, The Falcon and the Winter Soldier Ep. 1 Reactions AND Part 1 -- 2 hours and 40 minutes -- of Snydercut In Review are up on youtube.com/kindafunny and podcast services. Falcon is on Screencast.
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Mick @DaNanoBiologist Abrahamson, Black Jack, & Trent Berrie
